  </p>

  <h2>Our mission</h2>
  <p>
    Most platforms rent creators an audience and skim the value off the top. We think that's
    backwards. avaTOK is the unified creator marketplace where people earn from day one — go live to
    paying fans, sell 1:1 and group consults, launch an AI voice agent that earns while you sleep,
    and keep <strong>80%</strong> of what you make. One account, real people, your money your way.
  </p>

  <h2>AI-centric by design</h2>
  <p>
    We are an AI-centric software company. AI runs through everything we build — from voice agents
    and live translation to the tools that help creators run their business. We believe AI should
    work on <em>your</em> side of the glass: assisting you, never auctioning your attention.
  </p>
  <div class="note">
    A note on AI: our products use artificial intelligence, and AI can make mistakes. We share more
    in our <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>. We've also made our best efforts to use
    AI-generated imagery responsibly — if you ever find something objectionable, email
    <a href="mailto:support@avatok.ai">support@avatok.ai</a> and we'll remove it. It was never
    intentional.
  </p>

  <h2>What we value</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Creators first.</strong> You own your content, your data, and your audience.</li>
    <li><strong>Real people.</strong> Verification keeps the community genuine and safe.</li>
    <li><strong>Fair economics.</strong> Earn from day one and keep 80%, paid via PayPal or Wise.</li>
    <li><strong>Built responsibly.</strong> Privacy, safety, and honest AI are part of the product,
      not an afterthought.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>A global team</h2>
  <p>
    avaTOK is made with care by a distributed team of builders across the USA, India, the UK,
    Germany, and Vietnam. Want to help build the future of the creator economy? See our
    <a href="/careers">open roles</a>.
  </p>

